OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FEvening
OL,6,Fsunny periods giving way to clear
OL,7,Fspells for a time. Colder than the
OL,8,Fprevious night, with a widespread
OL,9,Ffrost developing, especially in rural
OL,10,Fareas. Clouding over from northwest
OL,11,Flater in the night, with temperatures
OL,12,Frallying.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FSoon generally cloudy, with a
OL,15,Flittle rain then edging southeast.
OL,16,FGradually becoming bright and breezy
OL,17,Fduring the afternoon, with sunny
OL,18,Fspells and the odd sharp shower,
OL,19,Fperhaps thundery. Near-normal
OL,20,Ftemperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
